00:23:46,240 --> 00:23:47,500
What are you thinking?

382
00:23:48,080 --> 00:23:50,140
I'm just afraid you can't sleep well.

383
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,490
I came to accompany you,

384
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,690
so that you can sleep comfortably.

385
00:23:59,560 --> 00:23:59,840
Oh.

386
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:00,680
Oh.

387
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:03,700
Good night.

388
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:07,420
Good night.

389
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:29,690
You want to give up Gu's shares forever

390
00:25:29,920 --> 00:25:31,280
just to not marry He Yue?

391
00:25:31,760 --> 00:25:32,680
Not just He Yue.

392
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:33,840
Dad,

393
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:35,320
I hope you can let me

394
00:25:35,320 --> 00:25:36,720
choose the person I love.

395
00:25:36,920 --> 00:25:38,780
What do you think Gu's shares are?

396
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:40,370
Is it a bargaining chip?

397
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:42,160
Do you still respect me?

398
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:45,080
Dad.

399
00:25:46,560 --> 00:25:47,890
Dad, I didn't mean that.

400
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,930
I don't want to marry He Yue.

401
00:25:50,080 --> 00:25:51,240
I like Qiao Yan.

402
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:51,880
Stop it.

403
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:55,930
Mind your own business.

404
00:25:56,800 --> 00:25:57,600
I'll deal with

405
00:25:58,080 --> 00:25:58,760
Yan.

406
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:01,320
Dad.

407
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:04,440
Yan and I really love each other.

408
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,560
You can beat me or scold me.

409
00:26:06,800 --> 00:26:07,800
But I beg you,

410
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:10,200
