411
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,480
Say it again!

412
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:13,280
Say it again!

413
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:18,120
Your brother and sister-in-law

414
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:19,780
