415
00:26:24,080 --> 00:26:24,480
What?

416
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:27,800
Can’t say it?

417
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:30,120
Yuan,

418
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,170
