419
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:34,740
Have you thought about it?

420
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:36,640
Once this matter is exposed,

421
00:26:37,040 --> 00:26:37,770
what will Yan

422
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:38,880
face,

423
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,320
and endure?

424
00:26:40,600 --> 00:26:41,680
I will protect her.

425
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,800
I will face it with her.

426
00:26:44,560 --> 00:26:45,440
As long as she is happy

427
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,200
and joyful,

428
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:48,400
I'm willing to give everything I have.

429
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,960
The public's judgment

430
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:51,360
goes on and on.

431
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:53,580
