433
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:58,000
Can you really guarantee that Yan

434
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,200
won't get hurt?

435
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:16,360
Jingyuan.

436
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:21,000
I'm doing this for your own good.

437
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:22,520
Tomorrow,

438
00:27:23,680 --> 00:27:25,880
at the signing ceremony with He family,

439
00:27:26,480 --> 00:27:27,360
I will announce

440
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:29,600
your marriage with He Yue.

441
00:27:31,600 --> 00:27:32,440
Don't be late.

442
00:27:50,440 --> 00:27:50,970
Grandpa.

443
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:53,440
Why aren't you two come for breakfast?

444
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:55,120
