445
00:27:55,120 --> 00:27:55,560
Yan.

446
00:27:56,080 --> 00:27:57,200
Follow me to the study.

447
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,800
I have something to tell you.

448
00:27:59,080 --> 00:27:59,480
Oh.

449
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:03,050
Grandpa.

450
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,580
Why do you suddenly want me
to change my surname?

451
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:08,180
You're my granddaughter.

452
00:28:08,760 --> 00:28:10,040
How can you a Qiao?

453
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:12,970
You'll be seen as a laughingstock.

454
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:13,640
But...

455
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,080
Does it really matter

456
00:28:15,080 --> 00:28:16,480
