457
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,560
My name was given by my dad.

458
00:28:20,120 --> 00:28:22,080
He wanted me to have my mom's last name.

459
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:22,960
You know that.

460
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:24,120
And you promised me

461
00:28:24,120 --> 00:28:25,480
