465
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:30,760
Grandpa.

466
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:31,600
Yan.

467
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:32,970
Listen to me.

468
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:42,520
I can't promise you this.

469
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:45,320
I love my parents.

470
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:48,890
I want to respect all their decisions.

471
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,560
They gave me this name.

472
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:53,560
I won't change it.

473
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:56,680
Okay.

474
00:28:57,680 --> 00:28:58,740
We'll discuss this

475
00:28:58,800 --> 00:28:59,840
later.

476
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:04,280
How have you been thinking about me

477
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:07,170
