478
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:09,520
Uh...

479
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:11,960
I...

480
00:29:13,000 --> 00:29:13,280
I...

481
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:14,480
I don't want to

